es/content/notification.html" class="dropdown-item"><small class="text-muted">Lorem ipsum (12/25/2017)</small><br><div>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet...</div></a><div class="dropdown-divider"></div><a href="/docs/pages/content/notifications.html" class="dropdown-item dropdown-link">See all notifications</a></div></li></ul></nav><nav><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="breadcrumb-item">Reference</li><li class="breadcrumb-item">Callout</li></ol></nav></div><div class="content-body"><div class="container"><h1>Callout</h1><p>Callouts provide contextual messages to draw attention of the user. See the examples below:</p><div class="callout mb-3"><h5>Basic</h5><p>I have a message for you, but not so important.</p></div><div class="callout callout-info mb-3"><h5>Good</h5><p>I have a message that may help you to understand better.</p></div><div class="callout callout-warning mb-3"><h5>Warning</h5><p>I have a warning for you. Be careful.</p></div><div class="callout callout-danger mb-3"><h5>Critital</h5><p>I have a critical message for you. This is really important.</p></div><div class="source-code"><a href="#callout-colors" data-toggle="collapse"><i class="fa fa-code"></i> Source code</a><div id="callout-colors" class="collapse"><pre><code class="html">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;callout&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h5&gt;Basic&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;I have a message for you, but not so important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;callout callout-info&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h5&gt;Good&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;I have a message that may help you to understand better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;callout callout-warning&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h5&gt;Warning&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;I have a warning for you. Be careful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;callout callout-danger&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h5&gt;Critital&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;I have a critical message for you. This is really important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/moment.js/2.22.1/moment.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.12.0/highlight.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.7.3/Chart.bundle.min.js"></script><script src="/dist/admin4b.min.js?v=2.1.0"></script><script src="/docs/assets/js/docs.js"></script></body></html>